text: Eduard Schlagintweit (23 March 1831 – 1866) was the third of the five Schlagintweit brothers of Munich. ==Life== He wrote an account of the 1859–1860 Spanish-Moroccan War. He was killed in the Battle of Kissingen, on 10 July 1866. ==References== ;Attribution * ==External links== * Category:Writers from Munich Category:1831 births Category:1866 deaths Category:German male writers
title: Eduard Schlagintweit
